Hi Georges,

Some people have been able to run an FI bus without an alternator for up 
to two hours at a time. There's a trip report in the list archives 
somewhere from Sean Bartnik back in 2000 or 2001 that describes it in 
some detail.

Me, I think it's the alternator.

Happy Trails,

